column2: SELECT TOP #   wiseXsdss.sdss_objid, wiseXsdss.wise_cntr, match_dist,  sdss_best.bestObjID, allwise.cntr FROM   WISE_xmatch wiseXsdss  JOIN   WISE_allsky allwise ON wiseXsdss.wise_cntr = allwise.cntr  JOIN   SpecObj sdss_best ON wiseXsdss.sdss_objid = sdss_best.bestObjID WHERE  sdss_best.class = &&&  AND sdss_best.zWarning = #  AND allwise.w1snr >= #  AND allwise.w2snr >= #  AND allwise.w1sat <= #  AND allwise.w1sat <= #  AND allwsie.w1mpro > #  AND allwsie.w2mpro > #  AND (allwise.glat < # OR allwise.glat > #)
